PRESS__________
Big Sky Partners Expands Unique Consulting Platform to Accelerate Brands, Empower Founders, and Provide Investments
‚ÄúI founded Big Sky Partners in response to tremendous demand by emerging companies and their investors for creative, nimble solutions to bridge a divide between creativity and capital,‚Äù said Smith, chief executive officer of Big Sky Partners. ‚ÄúFast-growing companies are facing a hyper-competitive environment for financial resources, market share and brand recognition, and Big Sky‚Äôs distinct platform provides a holistic solution with global reach.‚Äù 
